    ce "Acabamos de despejar el campo de batalla."

# game/episode021.rpy:492
translate spanish episode021_e0145965:

#   c "Good, not a moment too soon."
    c "Bien, no es demasiado pronto."

# game/episode021.rpy:493
translate spanish episode021_32122add:

#   c "Can you punch in a straight course toward Petrarch?"
    c "¿Puedes marcar un rumbo recto hacia Petrarca?"

# game/episode021.rpy:494
translate spanish episode021_309051c0:

#   ce "Done."
    ce "Hecho."

# game/episode021.rpy:499
translate spanish episode021_e829c4a5:

#   man "This is Captain Valinq of the Marleybone Irregulars."
    man "Este es el Capitán Valinq de los Irregulares de Marleybone."

# game/episode021.rpy:500
translate spanish episode021_22c6ca89:

#   man "I strongly suggest breaking off your current flight pattern and allowing us to pass undeterred."
    man "Le sugiero encarecidamente que rompa su patrón de vuelo actual y nos permita pasar sin inmutarnos."

# game/episode021.rpy:501
translate spanish episode021_3d9b9dd3:

#   "There was quite a long silence where the smaller ships were probably conferring among themselves."
    "Hubo un largo silencio en el que los barcos más pequeños probablemente estaban deliberando entre ellos."

# game/episode021.rpy:502
translate spanish episode021_c961b97a:

#   "Their deliberations didn't take very long though."
    "Pero sus deliberaciones no duraron mucho."

# game/episode021.rpy:503
translate spanish episode021_8a9b6ff1:

#   woman "Captain Valinq, you are hereby granted passage."
    woman "Capitán Valinq, se le concede el paso."

# game/episode021.rpy:505
translate spanish episode021_41617f04:

#   c "Well, all you have to do is be polite to them, I guess?"
    c "Bueno, todo lo que tienes que hacer es ser educado con ellos, supongo."

# game/episode021.rpy:506
translate spanish episode021_2c3b584d:

#   av "The name of the Irregulars also seems to carry a lot of weight."
    av "El nombre de los Irregulares también parece tener mucho peso."

# game/episode021.rpy:508
translate spanish episode021_4452731a:

#   "We weren’t bothered for the rest of our passing through the contested zone."
    "No nos molestaron durante el resto de nuestro paso por la zona disputada."

# game/episode021.rpy:511
translate spanish episode021_5e1b2cf2:

#   man "Iron Bastard, this is Captain Valinq speaking."
    man "Bastardo de Hierro, habla el Capitán Valinq."

# game/episode021.rpy:512
translate spanish episode021_0b339393:

#   man "This is as far as we'll go."
    man "Hasta aquí hemos llegado."

# game/episode021.rpy:513
translate spanish episode021_aee85058:

#   man "You should be able to reach your destination on your own from here."
    man "Desde aquí debería poder llegar a su destino por sus propios medios."

# game/episode021.rpy:514
translate spanish episode021_ffc21b44:

#   man "There’s a lone gateway, not far from here, which you should cross."
    man "Hay una puerta solitaria, no lejos de aquí, que deberías cruzar."

# game/episode021.rpy:515
translate spanish episode021_4b0ae93a:

#   man "It’s the only way into the system and shouldn’t be guarded."
    man "Es la única vía de entrada al sistema y no debería estar vigilada."

# game/episode021.rpy:516
translate spanish episode021_44893814:

#   man "As for getting back from Petrarch, I wish you the best of luck."
    man "En cuanto a la vuelta de Petrarca, le deseo mucha suerte."

# game/episode021.rpy:517
translate spanish episode021_23461983:

#   c "Thank you, Captain Valinq, for protecting us and for your...{w} uh...{w} final words of support..."
    c "Gracias, Capitán Valinq, por protegernos y por su...{w} uh...{w} palabras finales de apoyo..."

# game/episode021.rpy:519
translate spanish episode021_0e374e2c:

#   "The Marleybone Irregulars broke away and we were left to pursue our course to Petrarch."
    "Los Irregulares de Marleybone se separaron y nos dejaron seguir nuestro rumbo hacia Petrarca."

# game/episode021.rpy:520
translate spanish episode021_283a8108:

#   "The war theater we'd navigated earlier was replaced by an eerie silence as soon as we crossed the threshold into Petrarch territory."
    "El teatro de guerra por el que habíamos navegado antes fue sustituido por un inquietante silencio en cuanto cruzamos el umbral hacia el territorio de Petrarca."

# game/episode021.rpy:521
translate spanish episode021_8024c827:

#   "No signs of battle were visible, nor were there any ships in the vicinity."
    "No se veían señales de batalla ni había barcos en las inmediaciones."

# game/episode021.rpy:523
translate spanish episode021_81e7f09e:

#   ce "There’s only one object on our scanners and it appears to be the gate they were talking about."
    ce "Sólo hay un objeto en nuestros escáneres y parece ser la puerta de la que hablaban."

# game/episode021.rpy:524
translate spanish episode021_3df9ad8d:

#   c "Set a course and keep an eye out for unwelcome guests."
    c "Fije un rumbo y vigile a los invitados no deseados."

# game/episode021.rpy:526
translate spanish episode021_ea81ce4f:

#   ce "We’re approaching the gateway."
    ce "Nos acercamos a la puerta."

# game/episode021.rpy:527
translate spanish episode021_88bf991f:

#   c "No enemies in sight?"
    c "¿No hay enemigos a la vista?"

# game/episode021.rpy:528
translate spanish episode021_5f9be55c:

#   av "The area around the gate appears to be deserted."
    av "La zona alrededor de la puerta parece estar desierta."

# game/episode021.rpy:529
translate spanish episode021_f5eca7b8:

#   c "Céline, take us through in that case."
    c "Céline, llévanos a través en ese caso."

# game/episode021.rpy:534
translate spanish episode021_8e36a349:

#   "Our passage through the gateway was instant and the change in scenery a marked one."
    "Nuestro paso por la puerta fue instantáneo y el cambio de escenario, notable."

# game/episode021.rpy:535
translate spanish episode021_307f35d9:

#   av "Petrarch should come into view in a few minutes."
    av "Petrarca debería aparecer en unos minutos."

# game/episode021.rpy:536
translate spanish episode021_cc806eba:

#   av "No other ships on our scanners."
    av "No hay otras naves en nuestros escáneres."

# game/episode021.rpy:537
translate spanish episode021_11e73def:

#   c "Acknowledged."
    c "Reconocido."

# game/episode021.rpy:539
translate spanish episode021_e1d8444a:

#   "When the triple stars and our destination planet finally appeared, some of the crew let out an audible gasp."
    "Cuando por fin aparecieron las estrellas triples y nuestro planeta de destino, algunos miembros de la tripulación dejaron escapar un jadeo audible."

# game/episode021.rpy:540
translate spanish episode021_6e5de444:

#   "We were all well aware of the age of the star system, but Petrarch actually looked ancient."
    "Todos éramos conscientes de la edad del sistema estelar, pero Petrarca parecía realmente antiguo."

# game/episode021.rpy:541
translate spanish episode021_28043c8d:

#   "Maybe it had to do with the quality of the light emanating from the stars we knew were slowly dying, or a trick of the chemical makeup of the system."
    "Tal vez tuviera que ver con la calidad de la luz que emanaba de las estrellas que sabíamos que morían lentamente, o con un truco de la composición química del sistema."

# game/episode021.rpy:543
translate spanish episode021_1e33f9af:

#   ce "The final approach to Petrarch will take us a few hours."
    ce "La aproximación final a Petrarca nos llevará unas horas."

# game/episode021.rpy:544
translate spanish episode021_e561ebd5:

#   ce "I’ll message you all when we’re about to make the final approach."
    ce "Les enviaré un mensaje cuando estemos a punto de hacer la aproximación final."

# game/episode021.rpy:545
translate spanish episode021_14e7e0d5:

#   c "Yes, now is a good time to catch up on some sleep."
    c "Sí, ahora es un buen momento para dormir un poco."

# game/episode021.rpy:546
translate spanish episode021_51eeaed2:

#   c "Unless you all want to admire the dreariness in front of us."
    c "A menos que todos quieran admirar la monotonía que tenemos delante."

# game/episode021.rpy:547
translate spanish episode021_991013f7:

#   av "No, I’m good, sleep sounds a lot better."
    av "No, estoy bien, dormir suena mucho mejor."

# game/episode021.rpy:548
translate spanish episode021_356b5471:

#   "We left Céline to navigate the final stretch toward Petrarch."
    "Dejamos a Céline para recorrer el tramo final hacia Petrarca."

# game/episode021.rpy:562
translate spanish episode021_9a40a0ee:

#   "The comms crackled and Céline’s voice resounded throughout the ship."
    "Los comunicadores crepitaron y la voz de Céline resonó en toda la nave."

# game/episode021.rpy:563
translate spanish episode021_c154612c:

#   ce "Captain to the bridge, we’re nearing Petrarch."
    ce "Capitán al puente, nos acercamos a Petrarca."

# game/episode021.rpy:564
translate spanish episode021_87fa5f8d:

#   "When I joined Céline, the planet was already in our sights."
    "Cuando me incorporé a Céline, el planeta ya estaba en nuestro punto de mira."

# game/episode021.rpy:565
translate spanish episode021_71c39713:

#   "Just like we’d expected, Petrarch appeared to be a barren world."
    "Tal como esperábamos, Petrarca parecía un mundo estéril."

# game/episode021.rpy:566
translate spanish episode021_ea4c85c5:

#   "The ship’s scanners had detected large mountain ranges and a few oceans."
    "Los escáneres de la nave habían detectado grandes cadenas montañosas y algunos océanos."

# game/episode021.rpy:568
translate spanish episode021_7f328c28:

#   c "Any sign of life?"
    c "¿Alguna señal de vida?"

# game/episode021.rpy:569
translate spanish episode021_bb1a555a:

#   av "Not on the surface."
    av "No en la superficie."

# game/episode021.rpy:570
translate spanish episode021_827bba41:

#   av "However, I’m just now picking up a few energy signatures."
    av "Sin embargo, recién ahora estoy captando algunas firmas de energía."

# game/episode021.rpy:571
translate spanish episode021_11293f80:

#   c "What kind?"
    c "¿De qué tipo?"

# game/episode021.rpy:572
translate spanish episode021_a282efc7:

#   av "According to our scans, those appear to be power sources."
    av "Según nuestros escaneos, parecen ser fuentes de energía."

# game/episode021.rpy:573
translate spanish episode021_5e09a256:

#   c "What, like power generators?"
    c "¿Qué, como generadores de energía?"

# game/episode021.rpy:574
translate spanish episode021_49ffbb4e:

#   av "Yes, maybe."
    av "Sí, tal vez."

# game/episode021.rpy:575
translate spanish episode021_5e6d6b36:

#   c "But still no sign of life?"
    c "¿Pero aún no hay señales de vida?"

# game/episode021.rpy:576
translate spanish episode021_f5f6e081:

#   av "Nothing."
    av "Nada."

# game/episode021.rpy:577
translate spanish episode021_7166519c:

#   c "Weird."
    c "Raro."

# game/episode021.rpy:578
translate spanish episode021_ce620ca7:

#   c "Let’s check one of those sources out."
    c "Comprobemos una de esas fuentes."

# game/episode021.rpy:579
translate spanish episode021_2217bc63:

#   c "I want to know the second we are being targeted."
    c "Quiero saber en qué segundo nos están apuntando."

# game/episode021.rpy:580
translate spanish episode021_6885301d:

#   av "Acknowledged."
    av "Reconocido."

# game/episode021.rpy:581
translate spanish episode021_4a95702d:

#   ce "Approaching the nearest power source."
    ce "Acercándose a la fuente de energía más cercana."

# game/episode021.rpy:583
translate spanish episode021_f94449e6:

#   "The Bastard broke through the atmosphere and began its vector toward the energy signature."
    "El Bastardo atravesó la atmósfera e inició su vector hacia la firma energética."

# game/episode021.rpy:584
translate spanish episode021_e26452af:

#   "The mountain ranges indicated on our map now came into visual range."
    "Las cadenas montañosas indicadas en nuestro mapa entraban ahora en el campo visual."

# game/episode021.rpy:585
translate spanish episode021_dcee64cb:

#   "Long pillars of some type of black rock, hexagonal in shape, pierced the sky."
    "Largos pilares de algún tipo de roca negra, de forma hexagonal, atravesaban el cielo."

# game/episode021.rpy:586
translate spanish episode021_854c5fd2:

#   "Pools of oily water lapped against the base of those large rock columns."
    "Charcos de agua aceitosa chapoteaban contra la base de aquellas grandes columnas de roca."

# game/episode021.rpy:588
translate spanish episode021_8c0cd925:

#   "As the Bastard came nearer to our target, lights could be made out in the distance."
    "A medida que el Bastardo se acercaba a nuestro objetivo, se distinguían luces en la distancia."

# game/episode021.rpy:589
translate spanish episode021_3fcacb33:

#   c "Is that some kind of building?"
    c "¿Es algún tipo de edificio?"

# game/episode021.rpy:590
translate spanish episode021_80e90b06:

#   av "Looks like it."
    av "Eso parece."

# game/episode021.rpy:591
translate spanish episode021_55636436:

#   av "And the lights are on."
    av "Y las luces están encendidas."

# game/episode021.rpy:592
translate spanish episode021_4376155c:

#   c "I think we can definitively say that the power is still on over there."
    c "Creo que podemos decir definitivamente que la energía sigue allí."

# game/episode021.rpy:593
translate spanish episode021_48f2afbd:

#   c "Céline, can you set us down near one of those buildings?"
    c "Céline, ¿puedes dejarnos cerca de uno de esos edificios?"

# game/episode021.rpy:595
translate spanish episode021_1c54f831:

#   ce "Yes, there should be enough landing space."
    ce "Sí, debería haber suficiente espacio para aterrizar."

# game/episode021.rpy:596
translate spanish episode021_2340a0aa:

#   c "Okay crew, we’re going out."
    c "Bien tripulación, vamos a salir."

# game/episode021.rpy:597
translate spanish episode021_65417bee:

#   c "Aven, Eva, Jade and Thyia, suit up and meet me at the air lock."
    c "Aven, Eva, Jade y Thyia, preparaos y reuníos conmigo en la esclusa."

# game/episode021.rpy:599
translate spanish episode021_91448cc6:

#   "As we landed, Céline had some more information about the planet’s environment."
    "Cuando aterrizamos, Céline nos dio más información sobre el medio ambiente del planeta."

# game/episode021.rpy:600
translate spanish episode021_0a4d29c2:

#   "Temperatures, while not comfortable, were very much in range of human tolerances and the air was also breathable."
    "Las temperaturas, aunque no eran agradables, estaban muy dentro del rango de tolerancia humana y el aire también era respirable."

# game/episode021.rpy:601
translate spanish episode021_7bf84dee:

#   "My recon team first secured the immediate surroundings of the landing area."
    "Mi equipo de reconocimiento primero aseguró los alrededores inmediatos de la zona de aterrizaje."

# game/episode021.rpy:603
translate spanish episode021_a5d86ec5:

#   "The silence permeating everything was striking."
    "El silencio que lo impregnaba todo era sorprendente."

# game/episode021.rpy:604
translate spanish episode021_eae8cf1d:

#   th "I’ve never been in a place that appeared to be so dead."
    th "Nunca había estado en un lugar que pareciera tan muerto."

# game/episode021.rpy:605
translate spanish episode021_82ebbb87:

#   c "It sure seems that way."
    c "Eso parece."

# game/episode021.rpy:606
translate spanish episode021_d1218a24:

#   c "Let’s hope the planet doesn’t throw us some nasty surprises."
    c "Esperemos que el planeta no nos depare sorpresas desagradables."

# game/episode021.rpy:608
translate spanish episode021_14fe8f7d:

#   "Stairs were hewn from the black rock, the hexagonal shapes everywhere."
    "Las escaleras estaban talladas en la roca negra, con formas hexagonales por todas partes."

# game/episode021.rpy:609
translate spanish episode021_c756ffd0:

#   "As we climbed the stairs, the building came fully into view."
    "Al subir las escaleras, el edificio se hizo completamente visible."

# game/episode021.rpy:610
translate spanish episode021_fc7da065:

#   "A menacing structure of sharp angles, glossy black material, bathed in an angry red light."
    "Una amenazadora estructura de ángulos agudos, material negro brillante, bañada en una furiosa luz roja."

# game/episode021.rpy:612
translate spanish episode021_f8015877:

#   "The entrance to the building was clearly marked and we approached with our guns drawn."
    "La entrada al edificio estaba claramente señalizada y nos acercamos con las armas desenfundadas."

# game/episode021.rpy:613
translate spanish episode021_f4b65d8b:

#   th "Considering the power is on, I guess we should just hit the switch?"
    th "Teniendo en cuenta que hay corriente, supongo que deberíamos darle al interruptor."

# game/episode021.rpy:615
translate spanish episode021_845d15e1:

#   "Thyia indicated a glowing button next to the door."
    "Thyia indicó un botón luminoso junto a la puerta."

# game/episode021.rpy:616
translate spanish episode021_6910d647:

#   c "Be ready for anything."
    c "Esté preparado para todo."

# game/episode021.rpy:617
translate spanish episode021_f79c0cb3:

#   c "Thyia, on three..."
    c "Thyia, en tres..."

# game/episode021.rpy:618
translate spanish episode021_a3194e25:

#   c "One...{w} Two...{w} Three..."
    c "Uno...{w} Dos...{w} Tres..."

# game/episode021.rpy:620
translate spanish episode021_38c7f554:

#   "Thyia hit the button and the doors groaned open, revealing a glowing corridor beyond."
    "Thyia pulsó el botón y las puertas se abrieron con un gemido, revelando un pasillo resplandeciente."

# game/episode021.rpy:621
translate spanish episode021_67bad8c7:

#   "The opening of the door also punctured the unnatural quiet."
    "La apertura de la puerta también interrumpió el silencio antinatural."

# game/episode021.rpy:622
translate spanish episode021_b1419714:

#   "Inside, the mechanical sound of an air filtration system could be heard, as well as electronic murmuring from deeper inside the compound."
    "En el interior se oía el sonido mecánico de un sistema de filtración de aire, así como murmullos electrónicos procedentes del interior del recinto."

# game/episode021.rpy:623
translate spanish episode021_535ee7b0:

#   c "Let’s see if anyone is inside."
    c "Veamos si hay alguien dentro."

# game/episode021.rpy:625
translate spanish episode021_2bd57899:

#   "We entered the building and cleared the first sections of the corridor until we reached several doors."
    "Entramos en el edificio y despejamos los primeros tramos del pasillo hasta llegar a varias puertas."

# game/episode021.rpy:626
translate spanish episode021_df5ecfea:

#   "Both doors opened with the push of a button, giving access to empty rooms."
    "Ambas puertas se abrían pulsando un botón, dando acceso a habitaciones vacías."

# game/episode021.rpy:628
translate spanish episode021_55ad5d98:

#   "The lights came on as soon as we stepped inside to clear the room."
    "Las luces se encendieron en cuanto entramos para despejar la sala."

# game/episode021.rpy:629
translate spanish episode021_bde5bb06:

#   th "This seems to be a conference room."
    th "Esto parece ser una sala de conferencias."

# game/episode021.rpy:630
translate spanish episode021_ad602383:

#   "A large table encircled by several chairs stood in the middle of the room."
    "En el centro de la sala había una gran mesa rodeada de varias sillas."

# game/episode021.rpy:631
translate spanish episode021_482be926:

#   "No dust covered the surface of the table, nor the chairs, but for some reason the entire scene didn’t have a lived-in feeling."
    "Ni la superficie de la mesa ni las sillas estaban cubiertas de polvo, pero por alguna razón toda la escena no daba la sensación de estar habitada."

# game/episode021.rpy:633
translate spanish episode021_68817231:

#   av "I guess the cleaning systems are still operating?"
    av "¿Supongo que los sistemas de limpieza siguen funcionando?"

# game/episode021.rpy:635
translate spanish episode021_2003be3f:

#   th "Seems so."
    th "Eso parece."

# game/episode021.rpy:636
translate spanish episode021_9ec8e12e:

#   th "Yet I can’t shake the feeling that nobody has sat in those chairs for a long time."
    th "Sin embargo, no puedo evitar la sensación de que hace mucho tiempo que nadie se sienta en esas sillas."

# game/episode021.rpy:637
translate spanish episode021_1442a011:

#   j "The base consoles are operational as well."
    j "Las consolas base también están operativas."

# game/episode021.rpy:638
translate spanish episode021_2809e2cb:

#   c "Lets clear the entire building before getting into all that."
    c "Despejemos todo el edificio antes de entrar en eso."

# game/episode021.rpy:639
translate spanish episode021_3bef5c0d:

#   c "As soon as we’ve made sure there’s nobody around, the rest of the crew can come over as well."
    c "En cuanto nos hayamos asegurado de que no hay nadie, el resto de la tripulación puede venir también."

# game/episode021.rpy:641
translate spanish episode021_6508f8d2:

#   av "You’re thinking of setting up a base of operations here?"
    av "¿Piensas establecer aquí una base de operaciones?"

# game/episode021.rpy:642
translate spanish episode021_1893ff44:

#   c "Maybe, this building seems as good a place as any."
    c "Tal vez, este edificio parece un lugar tan bueno como cualquier otro."

# game/episode021.rpy:643
translate spanish episode021_2223d49d:

#   av "Agreed, from what I’ve seen outside, this building can be defended as well, if need be."
    av "De acuerdo, por lo que he visto fuera, este edificio también puede defenderse, si es necesario."

# game/episode021.rpy:644
translate spanish episode021_00e945a5:

#   c "Not looking forward to enduring a siege here, but good to know we’ve got options."
    c "No tengo ganas de soportar un asedio aquí, pero es bueno saber que tenemos opciones."

# game/episode021.rpy:646
translate spanish episode021_38590133:

#   "Our recon squad worked methodically across the entire first floor of the building, before entering the elevator to the second level."
    "Nuestro escuadrón de reconocimiento trabajó metódicamente por todo el primer piso del edificio, antes de entrar en el ascensor que conducía al segundo nivel."

# game/episode021.rpy:647
translate spanish episode021_44ff47ef:

#   "The second level was devoid of any life as well."
    "El segundo nivel también estaba desprovisto de vida."

# game/episode021.rpy:649
translate spanish episode021_24311f8f:

#   "We did find more rooms, including several living quarters and some sort of control room filled with computer consoles."
    "Encontramos más habitaciones, incluidos varios habitáculos y una especie de sala de control llena de consolas informáticas."

# game/episode021.rpy:650
translate spanish episode021_4f4069ab:

#   "The latter filled Jade with an almost unstoppable curiosity."
    "Esto último llenó a Jade de una curiosidad casi imparable."

# game/episode021.rpy:651
translate spanish episode021_79965870:

#   "All of the rooms were clean, even clinically so."
    "Todas las habitaciones estaban limpias, incluso clínicamente."

# game/episode021.rpy:652
translate spanish episode021_a4fde99a:

#   "No personal effects appeared to be present, nor any other detritus that would have indicated any humanoid habitation."
    "No parecía haber efectos personales ni otros restos que indicaran la presencia de algún humanoide."

# game/episode021.rpy:653
translate spanish episode021_271799a2:

#   "I was hoping Jade’s analysis of the building’s mainframe would provide some clues."
    "Esperaba que el análisis de Jade del ordenador central del edificio diera alguna pista."

# game/episode021.rpy:654
translate spanish episode021_a4d94d09:

#   "Otherwise we’d need to venture outside as soon as possible to map our surroundings."
    "De lo contrario, tendríamos que salir al exterior lo antes posible para cartografiar nuestro entorno."

# game/episode021.rpy:656
translate spanish episode021_2ede1a92:

#   "There was no indication of there being anything below the second floor, so after checking the entirety of it we signalled the rest of the crew to come join us."
    "No había indicios de que hubiera nada debajo del segundo piso, así que después de comprobarlo en su totalidad hicimos señas al resto de la tripulación para que se uniera a nosotros."

# game/episode021.rpy:657
translate spanish episode021_3628aa88:

#   "Everyone was assigned a personal room in the living area of the compound."
    "A cada uno se le asignó una habitación personal en la zona de estar del recinto."

# game/episode021.rpy:658
translate spanish episode021_621766e5:

#   "Jade got to work on the computers in the control room we’d found earlier, while Thyia began to inspect the internal systems of the base."
    "Jade se puso a trabajar en los ordenadores de la sala de control que habíamos encontrado antes, mientras Thyia empezaba a inspeccionar los sistemas internos de la base."

# game/episode021.rpy:659
translate spanish episode021_4a5cecef:

#   "That left us with some time to kill and the opportunity to plan our eventual expedition on the planet’s surface."
    "Eso nos dejó algo de tiempo para matar y la oportunidad de planear nuestra eventual expedición a la superficie del planeta."

# game/episode021.rpy:276
translate spanish episode021_337e5822_1:

#   ag "Goodbye, Mr. Von Skandersfeldt."
    ag "Adiós, Sr. Von Skandersfeldt."

# game/episode021.rpy:315
translate spanish episode021_a3be9cda_1:

#   ag "Good."
    ag "Bien."

# game/episode021.rpy:338
translate spanish episode021_57c18e97_1:

#   ag "Of course."
    ag "Por supuesto."

# game/episode021.rpy:362
translate spanish episode021_21a68b0a_1:

#   ag "Interesting."
    ag "Interesante."

# game/episode021.rpy:373
translate spanish episode021_e33793be_1:

#   bl "Of course, sir."
    bl "Por supuesto, señor."

# game/episode021.rpy:472
translate spanish episode021_6d9c3581_1:

#   ce "Not yet."
    ce "Todavía no."

# game/episode021.rpy:509
translate spanish episode021_1cbdca95_1:

#   "Gradually, the signs of destruction and the fleets of ships fighting in the distance faded."
    "Poco a poco, los signos de destrucción y las flotas de barcos luchando en la distancia se desvanecieron."

# game/episode021.rpy:677
translate spanish ep021_petrarch_choices_de8b5394:

#   "When we got back from visiting that unnerving pyramid, Eva and I decided to call a family meeting."
    "Cuando volvimos de visitar aquella inquietante pirámide, Eva y yo decidimos convocar una reunión familiar."

# game/episode021.rpy:679
translate spanish ep021_petrarch_choices_484c7c6f:

#   "When we got back from visiting that unnerving pyramid, Eva and I decided to call a meeting."
    "Cuando volvimos de visitar aquella inquietante pirámide, Eva y yo decidimos convocar una reunión."

# game/episode021.rpy:740
translate spanish ep021_petrarch_choices_5ce754d2:

#   "In order to fulfill my promise to Vess, I wanted a more neutral place to handle the breakups."
    "Para cumplir mi promesa a Vess, quería un lugar más neutral para tratar las rupturas."

# game/episode021.rpy:741
translate spanish ep021_petrarch_choices_9f90f058:

#   "I told them I would meet them in their quarters."
    "Les dije que me reuniría con ellos en sus habitaciones."

# game/episode021.rpy:743
translate spanish ep021_petrarch_choices_ed7fd93d:

#   "In order to fulfill my promise to Vess, I wanted a more neutral place to handle our breakup."
    "Para cumplir mi promesa a Vess, quería un lugar más neutral para tratar nuestra ruptura."

# game/episode021.rpy:744
translate spanish ep021_petrarch_choices_195cdae2:

#   "I told her I would meet her in her quarters."
    "Le dije que me reuniría con ella en sus aposentos."

# game/episode021.rpy:788
translate spanish ep021_temple_278adf93:

#   "After the necessary preparations, we set out to the location on the map."
    "Tras los preparativos necesarios, nos dirigimos al lugar indicado en el mapa."

# game/episode021.rpy:789
translate spanish ep021_temple_fc4d16c0:

#   "The trek proved to be rather difficult, due to the uneven terrain and slippery surfaces."
    "La caminata resultó bastante difícil, debido a las irregularidades del terreno y a las superficies resbaladizas."

# game/episode021.rpy:791
translate spanish ep021_temple_6b124bfb:

#   l "This is such a gloomy place."
    l "Este es un lugar tan sombrío."

# game/episode021.rpy:792
translate spanish ep021_temple_61ed7c35:

#   c "You can say that again."
    c "Puedes repetirlo."

# game/episode021.rpy:793
translate spanish ep021_temple_21bf7760:

#   l "Paclerara felt so alive, but this place is completely lifeless."
    l "Paclerara se sentía tan viva, pero este lugar carece por completo de vida."

# game/episode021.rpy:794
translate spanish ep021_temple_4376b716:

#   l "It even sounds dead."
    l "Incluso suena a muerto."

# game/episode021.rpy:795
translate spanish ep021_temple_e3dfadfe:

#   c "I know what you mean, silence never sounded so oppressive."
    c "Sé lo que quieres decir, el silencio nunca sonó tan opresivo."

# game/episode021.rpy:797
translate spanish ep021_temple_80e5157a:

#   "We continued to climb over the rough terrain, making steady progress towards our end goal."
    "Seguimos subiendo por el terreno accidentado, avanzando con paso firme hacia nuestro objetivo final."

# game/episode021.rpy:798
translate spanish ep021_temple_f26dfa2c:

#   "When we dropped from a ledge onto a large flat expanse, Eva let out a gasp."
    "Cuando caímos de un saliente a una gran llanura, Eva soltó un grito ahogado."

# game/episode021.rpy:800
translate spanish ep021_temple_c9d8b4db:

#   e "Is that what I think it is?"
    e "¿Es lo que creo que es?"

# game/episode021.rpy:801
translate spanish ep021_temple_1a570af3:

#   av "Those piles you mean?"
    av "¿Te refieres a esos montones?"

# game/episode021.rpy:802
translate spanish ep021_temple_e0d3420d:

#   e "Are those bones?"
    e "¿Son huesos?"

# game/episode021.rpy:804
translate spanish ep021_temple_514631a6:

#   "Eva was right, large piles of bones lay strewn across the terrain, the signs of possible previous habitation of the planet."
    "Eva tenía razón, grandes montones de huesos yacían esparcidos por el terreno, los signos de una posible habitabilidad anterior del planeta."

# game/episode021.rpy:805
translate spanish ep021_temple_cf6cc58c:

#   "There were so many bones scattered on the ground that we couldn’t help but step on them."
    "Había tantos huesos esparcidos por el suelo que no pudimos evitar pisarlos."

# game/episode021.rpy:806
translate spanish ep021_temple_087873dc:

#   "The mealy crushing and breaking sounds filled us all with disgust, but there was no other way forward."
    "Los sonidos de aplastamiento y rotura nos llenaban a todos de asco, pero no había otra salida."

# game/episode021.rpy:807
translate spanish ep021_temple_59518fd9:

#   c "Humanoid skeletons, I think?"
    c "¿Esqueletos humanoides, creo?"

# game/episode021.rpy:809
translate spanish ep021_temple_8625d3a6:

#   na "Yes, it appears so."
    na "Sí, eso parece."

# game/episode021.rpy:810
translate spanish ep021_temple_90c3c479:

#   na "All ancient, as far as I can tell."
    na "Todo antiguo, por lo que veo."

# game/episode021.rpy:811
translate spanish ep021_temple_055a55a3:

#   av "So this is some mass grave that somehow got excavated by some force?"
    av "¿Así que esto es una fosa común que de alguna manera fue excavada por alguna fuerza?"

# game/episode021.rpy:812
translate spanish ep021_temple_ddc19c4e:

#   na "No, I don’t think so."
    na "No, no lo creo."

# game/episode021.rpy:813
translate spanish ep021_temple_134a63c1:

#   c "This looks more like the remnants of a massacre."
    c "Esto se parece más a los restos de una masacre."

# game/episode021.rpy:815
translate spanish ep021_temple_1e6b7645:

#   l "So they murdered each other?"
    l "¿Así que se asesinaron entre ellos?"

# game/episode021.rpy:816
translate spanish ep021_temple_9d17c198:

#   e "Or they’re all victims and got killed by something else."
    e "O todos son víctimas y los mató otra cosa."

# game/episode021.rpy:817
translate spanish ep021_temple_bf5920ea:

#   c "Whatever happened, this planet grows more charming by the minute."
    c "Pasara lo que pasara, este planeta se vuelve más encantador a cada minuto."

# game/episode021.rpy:819
translate spanish ep021_temple_4cf77d26:

#   "We ventured on through the boneyard, until something glowing became visible on the horizon."
    "Nos aventuramos a través del cementerio, hasta que algo brillante se hizo visible en el horizonte."

# game/episode021.rpy:820
translate spanish ep021_temple_4f163967:

#   e "Are those the same type of crystal as the Key?"
    e "¿Son del mismo tipo de cristal que la Llave?"

# game/episode021.rpy:821
translate spanish ep021_temple_4f72a19b:

#   c "It sure looks the same."
    c "Seguro que tiene el mismo aspecto."

# game/episode021.rpy:823
translate spanish ep021_temple_86d5370a:

#   "The crystals were hovering above a large structure, a pyramid of sorts, built in the same unnerving style as the compound we were staying at."
    "Los cristales flotaban sobre una gran estructura, una especie de pirámide, construida con el mismo estilo inquietante que el complejo en el que nos alojábamos."

# game/episode021.rpy:824
translate spanish ep021_temple_8b150957:

#   "The grounds directly surrounding the pyramid were devoid of any skeletons, a peculiar contrast to the heaps of bones behind us."
    "En los alrededores de la pirámide no había esqueletos, lo que contrastaba con los montones de huesos que había detrás de nosotros."

# game/episode021.rpy:825
translate spanish ep021_temple_1b7c7e36:

#   "An entrance was clearly marked by lights and ornate archways, it didn’t at all look inviting."
    "La entrada, claramente marcada por luces y arcos ornamentados, no parecía en absoluto acogedora."

# game/episode021.rpy:827
translate spanish ep021_temple_2b6779bf:

#   e "Are we going inside?"
    e "¿Vamos a entrar?"

# game/episode021.rpy:828
translate spanish ep021_temple_532dea66:

#   c "I’d rather not, but according to the maps this was an important place."
    c "Preferiría no hacerlo, pero según los mapas este era un lugar importante."

# game/episode021.rpy:830
translate spanish ep021_temple_6893b3c4:

#   "We approached the temple, guns drawn and waited before the entrance doors."
    "Nos acercamos al templo con las armas desenfundadas y esperamos ante las puertas de entrada."

# game/episode021.rpy:832
translate spanish ep021_temple_9ef90280:

#   "Thyia slammed the button and the doors slowly groaned open."
    "Thyia apretó el botón y las puertas se abrieron lentamente."

# game/episode021.rpy:833
translate spanish ep021_temple_25e83ece:

#   "The corridor behind looked familiar, obviously the same build as the ones in our building, but larger."
    "El pasillo de detrás me resultaba familiar, obviamente de la misma construcción que los de nuestro edificio, pero más grande."

# game/episode021.rpy:834
translate spanish ep021_temple_e5c5b51a:

#   "Just as the compound we had set up as a base, this pyramid appeared to be devoid of any life."
    "Al igual que el complejo que habíamos establecido como base, esta pirámide parecía estar desprovista de toda vida."

# game/episode021.rpy:836
translate spanish ep021_temple_feb7b786:

#   "Quickly we cleared the corridor and adjacent rooms, arriving at a narrow staircase leading further up into the pyramid."
    "Despejamos rápidamente el pasillo y las salas adyacentes, llegando a una estrecha escalera que conducía más arriba en la pirámide."

# game/episode021.rpy:837
translate spanish ep021_temple_358237aa:

#   "After ascending the staircase, we found ourselves in a large circular room."
    "Tras subir la escalera, nos encontramos en una gran sala circular."

# game/episode021.rpy:839
translate spanish ep021_temple_360513a2:

#   "Spherical pods and all kinds of strange equipment surrounded something that looked both like a pedestal and a hospital bed."
    "Cápsulas esféricas y todo tipo de extraños equipos rodeaban algo que parecía a la vez un pedestal y una cama de hospital."

# game/episode021.rpy:841
translate spanish ep021_temple_847b2d09:

#   l "It looks like an operating theater."
    l "Parece un quirófano."

# game/episode021.rpy:842
translate spanish ep021_temple_2a72decc:

#   av "I was about to say that it looks like an arena with an altar in the middle."
    av "Iba a decir que parece una arena con un altar en el centro."

# game/episode021.rpy:844
translate spanish ep021_temple_28f7259e:

#   e "Whatever it was, this place gives me the creeps."
    e "Fuera lo que fuera, este lugar me da escalofríos."

# game/episode021.rpy:845
translate spanish ep021_temple_86b47164:

#   c "It sure is unnerving."
    c "Sí que es desconcertante."

# game/episode021.rpy:846
translate spanish ep021_temple_ac9c46f8:

#   c "Do those consoles still work, Jade?"
    c "¿Siguen funcionando esas consolas, Jade?"

# game/episode021.rpy:848
translate spanish ep021_temple_d20fa044:

#   j "Looks like it."
    j "Eso parece."

# game/episode021.rpy:849
translate spanish ep021_temple_8b09f11e:

#   j "Whatever is powering the devices in our compound is also keeping this building running."
    j "Lo que alimenta los dispositivos de nuestro complejo también mantiene en funcionamiento este edificio."

# game/episode021.rpy:850
translate spanish ep021_temple_e3c79a98:

#   th "Might be good to check those computers for clues."
    th "Sería bueno revisar esos ordenadores en busca de pistas."

# game/episode021.rpy:851
translate spanish ep021_temple_9030d8e4:

#   e "Do we really have to stay here?"
    e "¿De verdad tenemos que quedarnos aquí?"

# game/episode021.rpy:852
translate spanish ep021_temple_214e7d9c:

#   c "No, it might be best if we come back later."
    c "No, sería mejor que volviéramos más tarde."

# game/episode021.rpy:853
translate spanish ep021_temple_92a07f44:

#   c "We’ve wasted a lot of time getting here and there’s the journey back to consider as well."
    c "Hemos perdido mucho tiempo hasta llegar aquí y también hay que tener en cuenta el viaje de vuelta."

# game/episode021.rpy:854
translate spanish ep021_temple_0efeec4a:

#   c "There’s enough space to land the Bastard in the vicinity of the pyramid, so we’ll ask Céline to pilot us here tomorrow."
    c "Hay espacio suficiente para aterrizar el Bastardo en las inmediaciones de la pirámide, así que pediremos a Céline que nos pilote hasta aquí mañana."

# game/episode021.rpy:856
translate spanish ep021_temple_e140dec9:

#   "Everyone agreed and we began our journey back to the building where the others were waiting for us."
    "Todos estuvieron de acuerdo y emprendimos el camino de vuelta al edificio donde nos esperaban los demás."

# game/episode021.rpy:859
translate spanish ep021_temple_53883b61:

#   c "Are you okay, sis?"
    c "¿Estás bien, hermanita?"

# game/episode021.rpy:861
translate spanish ep021_temple_d79b52c0:

#   c "Are you okay, Eva?"
    c "¿Estás bien, Eva?"

# game/episode021.rpy:862
translate spanish ep021_temple_7f3bf486:

#   e "Yes, though I’m glad we’re out of that pyramid."
    e "Sí, aunque me alegro de que hayamos salido de esa pirámide."

# game/episode021.rpy:863
translate spanish ep021_temple_8315b9e9:

#   c "No more queasiness?"
    c "¿Se acabaron las náuseas?"

# game/episode021.rpy:864
translate spanish ep021_temple_5d28a474:

#   e "Thankfully no."
    e "Afortunadamente no."

# game/episode021.rpy:865
translate spanish ep021_temple_7e689c7c:

#   e "But bad things happened in that pyramid, [p_name_short], I just know it."
    e "Pero pasaron cosas malas en esa pirámide, [p_name_short], lo sé."

# game/episode021.rpy:866
translate spanish ep021_temple_610e04bf:

#   c "Well, like Lilly said, it looked like a surgery, but with a lot of room for an audience."
    c "Bueno, como dijo Lilly, parecía un quirófano, pero con mucho espacio para el público."

# game/episode021.rpy:867
translate spanish ep021_temple_64c05970:

#   c "I can’t imagine why you’d need a large audience to perform medical procedures."
    c "No puedo imaginar por qué se necesitaría una gran audiencia para realizar procedimientos médicos."

# game/episode021.rpy:869
translate spanish ep021_temple_ac6010f5:

#   na "That’s how they allowed students to learn about medical procedures in ancient times, I believe, hence the name “theater”."
    na "Así es como permitían a los estudiantes aprender sobre procedimientos médicos en la antigüedad, creo, de ahí el nombre de \"teatro\"."

# game/episode021.rpy:870
translate spanish ep021_temple_789e9108:

#   c "But they didn’t perform those procedures for arena crowds, did they?"
    c "Pero no realizaban esos procedimientos para las multitudes de los estadios, ¿verdad?"

# game/episode021.rpy:871
translate spanish ep021_temple_38615658:

#   na "I don’t think so."
    na "No lo creo."

# game/episode021.rpy:872
translate spanish ep021_temple_d22cfe96:

#   c "Maybe whatever they did in there had some religious meaning for whoever lived here once."
    c "Quizá lo que hicieran allí tuviera algún significado religioso para quien viviera aquí alguna vez."

# game/episode021.rpy:874
translate spanish ep021_temple_a86dc4e7:

#   e "Why does that make me think of live sacrifices?"
    e "¿Por qué me hace pensar en sacrificios en vida?"

# game/episode021.rpy:875
translate spanish ep021_temple_d2bd29cb:

#   e "Ugh, let’s just go back."
    e "Ugh, volvamos atrás."

# game/episode021.rpy:876
translate spanish ep021_temple_bc7835ed:

#   e "I can’t wait to leave this planet."
    e "No veo la hora de dejar este planeta."

# game/episode021.rpy:877
translate spanish ep021_temple_4011bb05:

#   c "No argument there."
    c "No hay discusión."

# game/episode021.rpy:884
translate spanish ep021_temple_return_a660f752:

#   "We returned to the temple the next day, Céline ferrying us over with the Bastard."
    "Volvimos al templo al día siguiente, Céline nos llevó con el Bastardo."

# game/episode021.rpy:885
translate spanish ep021_temple_return_cc303a9c:

#   "Eva opted to stay behind with several others, the place giving her the creeps."
    "Eva optó por quedarse atrás con varios otros, el lugar le daba escalofríos."

# game/episode021.rpy:886
translate spanish ep021_temple_return_58ac4094:

#   "I wasn’t planning on staying at the site longer than we had to, but we needed to investigate."
    "No pensaba quedarme en el sitio más tiempo del necesario, pero teníamos que investigar."

# game/episode021.rpy:888
translate spanish ep021_temple_return_c63139c9:

#   "Jade started working on the computers, while Thyia and Céline inspected the systems in the bowels of the temple."
    "Jade empezó a trabajar en los ordenadores, mientras Thyia y Céline inspeccionaban los sistemas en las entrañas del templo."

# game/episode021.rpy:890
translate spanish ep021_temple_return_67bdede1:

#   ki "I can see why Eva didn’t want to go with us."
    ki "Puedo ver por qué Eva no quería venir con nosotros."

# game/episode021.rpy:891
translate spanish ep021_temple_return_146d4388:

#   ki "Wish I had stayed behind as well."
    ki "Ojalá yo también me hubiera quedado."

# game/episode021.rpy:892
translate spanish ep021_temple_return_6c0a5800:

#   c "And here I thought you were going to provide some moral support."
    c "Y yo que pensaba que me ibas a dar apoyo moral."

# game/episode021.rpy:893
translate spanish ep021_temple_return_91e5af28:

#   ki "Nope, hate this place and I want to be gone as soon as possible."
    ki "No, odio este lugar y quiero irme lo antes posible."

# game/episode021.rpy:894
translate spanish ep021_temple_return_5d48eb07:

#   c "Go help Thyia and Céline then, I’ll keep watch here."
    c "Ve a ayudar a Thyia y Céline entonces, yo vigilaré aquí."

# game/episode021.rpy:895
translate spanish ep021_temple_return_dc60b772:

#   ki "Roger that."
    ki "Entendido."

# game/episode021.rpy:897
translate spanish ep021_temple_return_9dbb7757:

#   "Jade spent hours working on the computer consoles, Nadya helping her out where she could."
    "Jade se pasaba horas trabajando en las consolas del ordenador, y Nadya la ayudaba en lo que podía."

# game/episode021.rpy:899
translate spanish ep021_temple_return_392db8a9:

#   "Thyia and Céline eventually came back and reported nothing out of the ordinary."
    "Thyia y Céline acabaron volviendo y no informaron de nada fuera de lo normal."

# game/episode021.rpy:900
translate spanish ep021_temple_return_11aa47df:

#   "The temple was powered by the same technology we found in the compound we occupied as a base."
    "El templo estaba alimentado por la misma tecnología que encontramos en el recinto que ocupamos como base."

# game/episode021.rpy:902
translate spanish ep021_temple_return_a13f1f59:

#   j "Uh, [p_name], I think I’ve got something."
    j "Uh, [p_name], creo que tengo algo."

# game/episode021.rpy:904
translate spanish ep021_temple_return_9beef571:

#   j "Uh, [p_name_short], I think I’ve got something."
    j "Uh, [p_name_short], creo que tengo algo."

# game/episode021.rpy:905
translate spanish ep021_temple_return_d6f20865:

#   c "Let’s hear it."
    c "Un aplauso."

# game/episode021.rpy:907
translate spanish ep021_temple_return_6a34e504:

#   j "The console has some sort of simulation port we can interface with."
    j "La consola tiene algún tipo de puerto de simulación con el que podemos interactuar."

# game/episode021.rpy:908
translate spanish ep021_temple_return_01cfd372:

#   j "And there’s simulation data available in the system."
    j "Y hay datos de simulación disponibles en el sistema."

# game/episode021.rpy:909
translate spanish ep021_temple_return_ab56a972:

#   c "Do you know what it’s about?"
    c "¿Sabes de qué se trata?"

# game/episode021.rpy:910
translate spanish ep021_temple_return_bc96ef01:

#   j "No, the only way to find out is to enter the simulation."
    j "No, la única forma de averiguarlo es entrar en la simulación."

# game/episode021.rpy:911
translate spanish ep021_temple_return_6f4bcddf:

#   c "Yeah, not doing that."
    c "Sí, no hacer eso."

# game/episode021.rpy:912
translate spanish ep021_temple_return_878a13cb:

#   c "I don’t want to get trapped in an alien sim."
    c "No quiero quedarme atrapado en una simulación alienígena."

# game/episode021.rpy:914
translate spanish ep021_temple_return_4a20a54c:

#   th "The simulation hardware isn’t as advanced as ours."
    th "El hardware de simulación no es tan avanzado como el nuestro."

# game/episode021.rpy:915
translate spanish ep021_temple_return_1ab4c766:

#   th "It’s rather primitive, to be honest."
    th "Es bastante primitivo, la verdad."

# game/episode021.rpy:916
translate spanish ep021_temple_return_23e6149f:

#   th "No neural interface or other cortex stimulation."
    th "Sin interfaz neural ni otro tipo de estimulación del córtex."

# game/episode021.rpy:918
translate spanish ep021_temple_return_5d39b4f5:

#   j "Yes, this is really old technology."
    j "Sí, es una tecnología muy antigua."

# game/episode021.rpy:920
translate spanish ep021_temple_return_8cd2f190:

#   na "I believe it was called virtual reality at some point?"
    na "Creo que en algún momento se llamó realidad virtual."

# game/episode021.rpy:922
translate spanish ep021_temple_return_0ddde392:

#   th "A really misleading term, but yeah."
    th "Un término realmente engañoso, pero sí."

# game/episode021.rpy:923
translate spanish ep021_temple_return_84a98a46:

#   th "People apparently wore glasses that projected computer generated imagery."
    th "Al parecer, la gente llevaba gafas que proyectaban imágenes generadas por ordenador."

# game/episode021.rpy:924
translate spanish ep021_temple_return_9db6dcdb:

#   c "Quaint."
    c "Pintoresco."

# game/episode021.rpy:925
translate spanish ep021_temple_return_df9fc0d2:

#   th "Cutting-edge at some point in history."
    th "Vanguardista en algún momento de la historia."

# game/episode021.rpy:926
translate spanish ep021_temple_return_1d09338b:

#   c "So were cave paintings."
    c "También las pinturas rupestres."

# game/episode021.rpy:927
translate spanish ep021_temple_return_b6310296:

#   c "Alright, if there’s no risk of getting trapped we should check it out."
    c "De acuerdo, si no hay riesgo de quedar atrapados deberíamos comprobarlo."

# game/episode021.rpy:929
translate spanish ep021_temple_return_f710591c:

#   j "I’ll prepare the system."
    j "Prepararé el sistema."

# game/episode021.rpy:930
translate spanish ep021_temple_return_7fc2306a:

#   c "How many of us can go in?"
    c "¿Cuántos podemos entrar?"

# game/episode021.rpy:931
translate spanish ep021_temple_return_381e63b4:

#   j "The interface allows three parallel connections."
    j "La interfaz permite tres conexiones paralelas."

# game/episode021.rpy:933
translate spanish ep021_temple_return_8388c0a8:

#   c "Right, Mom and Thyia should come with, I think."
    c "Bien, mamá y Thyia deberían venir, creo."

# game/episode021.rpy:935
translate spanish ep021_temple_return_ecda8c3a:

#   c "Right, Nadya and Thyia should come with, I think."
    c "Bien, Nadya y Thyia deberían venir, creo."

# game/episode021.rpy:936
translate spanish ep021_temple_return_c19f2570:

#   c "Jade, you monitor the system and the rest can watch over us."
    c "Jade, tú vigila el sistema y el resto puede vigilarnos a nosotros."

# game/episode021.rpy:938
translate spanish ep021_temple_return_8051946a:

#   "Jade primed the system for us, while Thyia and Nadya prepared to enter the simulation."
    "Jade preparó el sistema para nosotros, mientras Thyia y Nadya se preparaban para entrar en la simulación."

# game/episode021.rpy:939
translate spanish ep021_temple_return_2b000b48:

#   j "The sim is ready."
    j "La simulación está lista."

# game/episode021.rpy:940
translate spanish ep021_temple_return_adccdb42:

#   j "Please use the headsets available."
    j "Utilice los auriculares disponibles."

# game/episode021.rpy:942
translate spanish ep021_temple_return_ddbeb393:

#   "Nothing seemed to change when we put the sets on our heads."
    "Nada parecía cambiar cuando nos poníamos los conjuntos en la cabeza."

# game/episode021.rpy:944
translate spanish ep021_temple_return_9884b7f7:

#   "But then visuals projected by our headsets began to cover our view, making the others fade away slowly."
    "Pero entonces los visuales proyectados por nuestros auriculares empezaron a cubrir nuestra vista, haciendo que los demás se desvanecieran lentamente."

# game/episode021.rpy:946
translate spanish ep021_temple_return_06264f81:

#   "The chamber now appeared to be empty, until an alien stepped into view."
    "La cámara parecía ahora vacía, hasta que apareció un alienígena."

# game/episode021.rpy:947
translate spanish ep021_temple_return_720f1cac:

#   "When the alien spoke, it did so in an unfamiliar language."
    "Cuando el alienígena habló, lo hizo en un idioma desconocido."

# game/episode021.rpy:948
translate spanish ep021_temple_return_e80f91e7:

#   "Strange guttural sounds emanated from the creature, which should have been unintelligible, but the three of us seemed to understand perfectly."
    "De la criatura emanaban extraños sonidos guturales, que deberían haber sido ininteligibles, pero los tres parecíamos entender perfectamente."

# game/episode021.rpy:951
translate spanish ep021_temple_return_d5c949ba:

#   shk "Welcome, your arrival has been eagerly anticipated..."
    shk "Bienvenido, su llegada ha sido muy esperada..."

# game/episode021.rpy:958
translate spanish ep021_jade_talk_6c0645d3:

#   "Jade had successfully breached the systems of the base and was now working with Céline to get some useful data."
    "Jade había logrado penetrar en los sistemas de la base y ahora trabajaba con Céline para obtener datos útiles."

# game/episode021.rpy:960
translate spanish ep021_jade_talk_ef1825af:

#   c "So locking yourself up inside this control room finally paid off?"
    c "¿Así que encerrarte en esta sala de control por fin ha valido la pena?"

# game/episode021.rpy:961
translate spanish ep021_jade_talk_ac2ed105:

#   j "I think so."
    j "Creo que sí."

# game/episode021.rpy:962
translate spanish ep021_jade_talk_1aa983d1:

#   j "The user interface of the system is not in any language I know."
    j "La interfaz de usuario del sistema no está en ningún idioma que yo conozca."

# game/episode021.rpy:963
translate spanish ep021_jade_talk_061b4566:

#   j "But I managed to pull up some imagery, just by trying out different key combinations."
    j "Pero me las arreglé para sacar algunas imágenes, simplemente probando diferentes combinaciones de teclas."

# game/episode021.rpy:964
translate spanish ep021_jade_talk_3e36dcaf:

#   j "Those images appear to be maps of this place."
    j "Esas imágenes parecen ser mapas de este lugar."

# game/episode021.rpy:965
translate spanish ep021_jade_talk_b38f535c:

#   j "According to Céline they line up with what little the Bastard’s sensors can pick up."
    j "Según Céline se alinean con lo poco que pueden captar los sensores del Bastardo."

# game/episode021.rpy:966
translate spanish ep021_jade_talk_74fe7148:

#   c "Anything interesting on those maps?"
    c "¿Algo interesante en esos mapas?"

# game/episode021.rpy:968
translate spanish ep021_jade_talk_28c53a23:

#   j "There are lots of places on those maps, but without a legend in a language we can read it’s fairly impossible to determine anything."
    j "Hay muchos lugares en esos mapas, pero sin una leyenda en un idioma que podamos leer es bastante imposible determinar nada."

# game/episode021.rpy:969
translate spanish ep021_jade_talk_569f9d48:

#   c "So we need to visit all those places?"
    c "¿Así que tenemos que visitar todos esos lugares?"

# game/episode021.rpy:970
translate spanish ep021_jade_talk_d55c2753:

#   j "That’s what Céline and I feared at first."
    j "Eso es lo que Céline y yo temíamos al principio."

# game/episode021.rpy:972
translate spanish ep021_jade_talk_cd911189:

#   j "But there’s one place that appears on all those maps and is consistently marked differently than the other points of interest."
    j "Pero hay un lugar que aparece en todos esos mapas y que siempre está marcado de forma diferente a los demás puntos de interés."

# game/episode021.rpy:973
translate spanish ep021_jade_talk_f6a9b118:

#   c "The planet’s capital?"
    c "¿La capital del planeta?"

# game/episode021.rpy:975
translate spanish ep021_jade_talk_92713d00:

#   j "Maybe."
    j "Tal vez."

# game/episode021.rpy:976
translate spanish ep021_jade_talk_fb09acd6:

#   j "Though a lot of other places seem to be connected somehow."
    j "Aunque muchos otros lugares parecen estar conectados de alguna manera."

# game/episode021.rpy:977
translate spanish ep021_jade_talk_bb259c92:

#   c "Like a network?"
    c "¿Como una red?"

# game/episode021.rpy:978
translate spanish ep021_jade_talk_131c2ccf:

#   j "Something like that."
    j "Algo así."

# game/episode021.rpy:979
translate spanish ep021_jade_talk_9596e5d8:

#   c "Is that spot far from here?"
    c "¿Ese lugar está lejos de aquí?"

# game/episode021.rpy:981
translate spanish ep021_jade_talk_31f28fd0:

#   j "We seem to have landed quite near, so the place can probably be reached on foot."
    j "Parece que hemos aterrizado bastante cerca, así que probablemente se pueda llegar al lugar a pie."

# game/episode021.rpy:982
translate spanish ep021_jade_talk_5bc2b85c:

#   c "Good, I think it’s time for an expedition."
    c "Bien, creo que es hora de una expedición."

# game/episode021.rpy:983
translate spanish ep021_jade_talk_ada92a2a:

#   c "I’ll inform the others."
    c "Informaré a los demás."

# game/episode021.rpy:992
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_5109fbff:

#   "I was surprised to find my mother lying in her sleepwear on the couch when I entered my quarters."
    "Me sorprendió encontrar a mi madre tumbada en ropa de dormir en el sofá cuando entré en mis aposentos."

# game/episode021.rpy:993
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_83a242ed:

#   c "Mom?"
    c "¿Mamá?"

# game/episode021.rpy:995
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_693386a5:

#   "I was surprised to find Nadya lying in her sleepwear on the couch when I entered my quarters."
    "Me sorprendió encontrar a Nadya tumbada en ropa de dormir en el sofá cuando entré en mis aposentos."

# game/episode021.rpy:996
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_011bb546:

#   c "Nadya?"
    c "¿Nadya?"

# game/episode021.rpy:998
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_b55634e2:

#   na "Oh!"
    na "¡Oh!"

# game/episode021.rpy:999
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_b6639dbd:

#   na "Sorry, I must have fallen asleep."
    na "Lo siento, debo haberme quedado dormido."

# game/episode021.rpy:1000
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_74354afe:

#   c "Were you waiting on me?"
    c "¿Me estabas esperando?"

# game/episode021.rpy:1002
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_9e99c962:

#   na "Yes, I wanted to talk to you."
    na "Sí, quería hablar contigo."

# game/episode021.rpy:1003
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_8500ba66:

#   na "But you were gone for a long time and I must have dozed off."
    na "Pero te fuiste por mucho tiempo y debo haberme quedado dormido."

# game/episode021.rpy:1006
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_c689fa2a:

#   na "I just wanted to congratulate you and Eva again."
    na "Sólo quería felicitaros a ti y a Eva de nuevo."

# game/episode021.rpy:1007
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_76a92099:

#   na "This is such a special moment for you both."
    na "Este es un momento tan especial para los dos."

# game/episode021.rpy:1009
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_f7c2eef3:

#   na "And for me as a future grandmother as well."
    na "Y también para mí como futura abuela."

# game/episode021.rpy:1010
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_e897fbb0:

#   c "Thank you."
    c "Gracias, señor."

# game/episode021.rpy:1011
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_5327cc36:

#   na "Please do not hesitate to rely on me for any help you need."
    na "No dude en contar conmigo para cualquier ayuda que necesite."

# game/episode021.rpy:1013
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_d461082b:

#   na "And I’m sure your sisters will be happy to help as well."
    na "Y estoy segura de que tus hermanas también estarán encantadas de ayudarte."

# game/episode021.rpy:1017
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_1de8a9d9:

#   na "Even Lilly and Aven, once they come around to accepting the situation."
    na "Incluso Lilly y Aven, una vez que acepten la situación."

# game/episode021.rpy:1018
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_ab559597:

#   c "I certainly hope they will."
    c "Espero que lo hagan."

# game/episode021.rpy:1019
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_2c63ba57:

#   na "It takes time."
    na "Lleva su tiempo."

# game/episode021.rpy:1020
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_07d09874:

#   na "Besides, there’s not much else they can do."
    na "Además, no pueden hacer mucho más."

# game/episode021.rpy:1022
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_a777fe68:

#   na "Even Lilly, once she comes around to accepting the situation."
    na "Incluso Lilly, una vez que acepte la situación."

# game/episode021.rpy:1023
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_35151593:

#   c "I certainly hope she will."
    c "Espero que lo haga."

# game/episode021.rpy:1025
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_1f0fc5ad:

#   na "Besides, there’s not much else she can do."
    na "Además, no puede hacer mucho más."

# game/episode021.rpy:1027
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_a90908db:

#   na "Even Aven, once she comes around to accepting the situation."
    na "Incluso Aven, una vez que acepte la situación."

# game/episode021.rpy:1031
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_d2e53bb9:

#   c "I just wish I can provide Eva with everything she needs."
    c "Sólo deseo poder proporcionar a Eva todo lo que necesita."

# game/episode021.rpy:1032
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_9e4ef2d0:

#   c "Considering the life we lead, it’s not going to be easy."
    c "Teniendo en cuenta la vida que llevamos, no va a ser fácil."

# game/episode021.rpy:1034
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_1c849bf4:

#   na "I will admit that we’re in a peculiar position, but being young parents is never easy."
    na "Admito que estamos en una situación peculiar, pero ser padres jóvenes nunca es fácil."

# game/episode021.rpy:1035
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_2c2b31f3:

#   na "You’ll both find a way, I’m sure of it."
    na "Ambos encontrarán una manera, estoy seguro de ello."

# game/episode021.rpy:1036
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_548818a8:

#   na "We’re so focused on pursuing this prophecy that all else seems to lose its importance."
    na "Estamos tan centrados en perseguir esta profecía que todo lo demás parece perder su importancia."

# game/episode021.rpy:1037
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_dcbffe65:

#   na "But anything threatens Eva or your baby, we will do everything to make sure she’s safe."
    na "Pero si algo amenaza a Eva o a tu bebé, haremos todo lo posible para que esté a salvo."

# game/episode021.rpy:1038
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_5f867242:

#   na "We’ll help you, every step of the way."
    na "Le ayudaremos en todo momento."

# game/episode021.rpy:1040
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_46e261f9:

#   c "Thanks, Mom, that means a lot."
    c "Gracias, mamá, eso significa mucho."

# game/episode021.rpy:1041
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_05e5c179:

#   c "I hope we’ll make you a proud grandmother."
    c "Espero que te convirtamos en una abuela orgullosa."

# game/episode021.rpy:1043
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_8ab187bf:

#   na "I already am."
    na "Ya lo estoy haciendo."

# game/episode021.rpy:1045
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_191fae03:

#   c "Thanks, Nadya, that means a lot."
    c "Gracias, Nadya, eso significa mucho."

# game/episode021.rpy:1047
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_512fa890:

#   na "Now, I’m going back to my quarters and see if I can catch some sleep in my own bed."
    na "Ahora vuelvo a mis aposentos a ver si duermo un poco en mi cama."

# game/episode021.rpy:1048
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_e2414be7:

#   na "Sleeping on that couch has done a number on my neck."
    na "Dormir en ese sofá ha hecho mella en mi cuello."

# game/episode021.rpy:1049
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_7f0bc750:

#   c "I hope you get some rest."
    c "Espero que descanses."

# game/episode021.rpy:1051
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_328be262:

#   c "Goodnight, Mom."
    c "Buenas noches, mamá."

# game/episode021.rpy:1053
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_fdd9b536:

#   c "Goodnight, Nadya."
    c "Buenas noches, Nadya."

# game/episode021.rpy:1054
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_47415891:

#   na "Goodnight, sweetheart."
    na "Buenas noches, cariño."

# game/episode021.rpy:1056
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_4589784a:

#   na "I wanted to have a word with you."
    na "Quería hablar contigo."

# game/episode021.rpy:1057
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_5a5c28b7:

#   na "About the news you and Eva shared earlier."
    na "Sobre las noticias que tú y Eva compartisteis antes."

# game/episode021.rpy:1058
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_7b7a5678:

#   c "Yes, of course."
    c "Sí, por supuesto."

# game/episode021.rpy:1060
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_872015af:

#   na "I’m sorry if I reacted harshly, but you must know that it was such a shock."
    na "Lo siento si reaccioné con dureza, pero debes saber que fue un shock."

# game/episode021.rpy:1061
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_24366554:

#   c "I understand."
    c "Entiendo."

# game/episode021.rpy:1063
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_38ae1404:

#   na "I know I’m not one to judge, considering what happened between Agust and me."
    na "Sé que no soy quién para juzgar, teniendo en cuenta lo que pasó entre Agust y yo."

# game/episode021.rpy:1064
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_cf622d4a:

#   na "But I do hope that you have both thought about the implications."
    na "Pero espero que ambos hayan pensado en las implicaciones."

# game/episode021.rpy:1065
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_8eecb102:

#   c "We have and decided it’s worth the sacrifice."
    c "Lo hemos hecho y hemos decidido que merece la pena el sacrificio."

# game/episode021.rpy:1067
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_ccb084fe:

#   na "Good."
    na "Bien."

# game/episode021.rpy:1068
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_4a8d89e3:

#   na "And I’ll support to you in any way I can."
    na "Y te apoyaré en todo lo que pueda."

# game/episode021.rpy:1070
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_80babbf7:

#   na "I can’t speak for your sisters, though."
    na "Aunque no puedo hablar por tus hermanas."

# game/episode021.rpy:1071
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_da0d7922:

#   na "They might need more time to accept."
    na "Puede que necesiten más tiempo para aceptarlo."

# game/episode021.rpy:1073
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_c40a80d2:

#   na "I can’t speak for your sister, though."
    na "Aunque no puedo hablar por tu hermana."

# game/episode021.rpy:1074
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_6ef12a77:

#   na "She might need more time to accept."
    na "Puede que necesite más tiempo para aceptarlo."

# game/episode021.rpy:1075
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_b6039869:

#   na "In any case, you’re exposing you both to a lot of danger."
    na "En cualquier caso, os estáis exponiendo los dos a mucho peligro."

# game/episode021.rpy:1076
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_cd44db39:

#   na "Incest isn’t accepted in most civilizations, human or otherwise."
    na "El incesto no se acepta en la mayoría de las civilizaciones, humanas o no."

# game/episode021.rpy:1077
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_8a6bc7ba:

#   na "So you might face ridicule or even prosecution at the very worst."
    na "En el peor de los casos, podría hacer el ridículo e incluso ser procesado."

# game/episode021.rpy:1078
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_fab27ad6:

#   c "We’re aware."
    c "Somos conscientes."

# game/episode021.rpy:1079
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_63ef8d3b:

#   na "Good, I just wanted to make that clear."
    na "Bien, sólo quería dejarlo claro."

# game/episode021.rpy:1080
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_481bbb52:

#   na "Because it’s in addition to the danger we find ourselves in, being on the run from the Sovereignty and all."
    na "Porque se suma al peligro en el que nos encontramos, al estar huyendo de la Soberanía y todo eso."

# game/episode021.rpy:1082
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_27f6eed2:

#   na "We all lead dangerous lives, with being on the run from the Sovereignty and all."
    na "Todos llevamos vidas peligrosas, huyendo de la Soberanía y todo eso."

# game/episode021.rpy:1083
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_cdaacdd8:

#   na "Once Eva’s pregnancy develops, she might need extra care."
    na "Una vez que el embarazo de Eva se desarrolle, podría necesitar cuidados adicionales."

# game/episode021.rpy:1084
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_ce3d91c6:

#   na "Or she might not be able to participate in any field missions."
    na "O puede que no pueda participar en ninguna misión sobre el terreno."

# game/episode021.rpy:1086
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_9dbb0dc1:

#   na "Thim might be able to assist when it comes to medical matters and I’m sure the crew will pitch in when it comes to additional support, when necessary."
    na "Thim podría ayudar en cuestiones médicas y estoy seguro de que la tripulación colaborará cuando sea necesario."

# game/episode021.rpy:1088
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_89a5fc66:

#   na "I’m sure the crew will pitch in when it comes to additional support, when necessary."
    na "Estoy seguro de que la tripulación colaborará cuando sea necesario."

# game/episode021.rpy:1089
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_07d91596:

#   na "We’re so focused on pursuing this prophecy, that all else seems to lose its importance."
    na "Estamos tan centrados en perseguir esta profecía, que todo lo demás parece perder su importancia."

# game/episode021.rpy:1094
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_ce04f979:

#   c "Thanks, that means a lot."
    c "Gracias, eso significa mucho."

# game/episode021.rpy:1101
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_d0e4210d:

#   na "Goodnight, son."
    na "Buenas noches, hijo."

# game/episode021.rpy:1104
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_9f7c045d:

#   na "Goodnight."
    na "Buenas noches."

# game/episode021.rpy:1024
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_2c63ba57_1:

#   na "It takes time."
    na "Lleva su tiempo."

# game/episode021.rpy:1029
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_2c63ba57_2:

#   na "It takes time."
    na "Lleva su tiempo."

# game/episode021.rpy:1028
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_35151593_1:

#   c "I certainly hope she will."
    c "Espero que lo haga."

# game/episode021.rpy:1030
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_1f0fc5ad_1:

#   na "Besides, there’s not much else she can do."
    na "Además, no puede hacer mucho más."

# game/episode021.rpy:1090
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_dcbffe65_1:

#   na "But anything threatens Eva or your baby, we will do everything to make sure she’s safe."
    na "Pero si algo amenaza a Eva o a tu bebé, haremos todo lo posible para que esté a salvo."

# game/episode021.rpy:1092
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_46e261f9_1:

#   c "Thanks, Mom, that means a lot."
    c "Gracias, mamá, eso significa mucho."

# game/episode021.rpy:1096
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_512fa890_1:

#   na "Now, I’m going back to my quarters and see if I can catch some sleep in my own bed."
    na "Ahora vuelvo a mis aposentos a ver si duermo un poco en mi cama."

# game/episode021.rpy:1097
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_e2414be7_1:

#   na "Sleeping on that couch has done a number on my neck."
    na "Dormir en ese sofá ha hecho mella en mi cuello."

# game/episode021.rpy:1098
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_7f0bc750_1:

#   c "I hope you get some rest."
    c "Espero que descanses."

# game/episode021.rpy:1100
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_328be262_1:

#   c "Goodnight, Mom."
    c "Buenas noches, mamá."

# game/episode021.rpy:1103
translate spanish ep021_nadya_talk_petrarch_fdd9b536_1:

#   c "Goodnight, Nadya."
    c "Buenas noches, Nadya."

# game/episode021.rpy:1111
translate spanish ep021_lilly_talk_c0530c6f:

#   "Lilly was reading on her tablet in one of the conference rooms."
    "Lilly estaba leyendo en su tableta en una de las salas de conferencias."

# game/episode021.rpy:1112
translate spanish ep021_lilly_talk_b2f58514:

#   c "I take it you’re not studying for your Academy exams?"
    c "¿Supongo que no estás estudiando para los exámenes de la Academia?"

# game/episode021.rpy:1114
translate spanish ep021_lilly_talk_95bc16f2:

#   l "Haha, no, I think we’re long past that, thankfully."
    l "Jaja, no, creo que eso ya lo hemos superado, por suerte."

# game/episode021.rpy:1116
translate spanish ep021_lilly_talk_f8b92cda:

#   l "I was just reading up on some news stories."
    l "Estaba leyendo algunas noticias."

# game/episode021.rpy:1117
translate spanish ep021_lilly_talk_9db6dc9a:

#   c "Are you able to connect to the Web from here?"
    c "¿Puedes conectarte a la Web desde aquí?"

# game/episode021.rpy:1119
translate spanish ep021_lilly_talk_b1bfe993:

#   l "No, we’re too far out for that."
    l "No, estamos demasiado lejos para eso."

# game/episode021.rpy:1120
translate spanish ep021_lilly_talk_a758b994:

#   l "But I saved some stories back when we were still in range."
    l "Pero guardé algunas historias de cuando aún estábamos a tiro."

# game/episode021.rpy:1121
translate spanish ep021_lilly_talk_e2863533:

#   c "Didn’t know you were so on top of things."
    c "No sabía que estabas tan al tanto de todo."

# game/episode021.rpy:1122
translate spanish ep021_lilly_talk_f7503e3a:

#   l "I’m not, but I get curious about what’s happening back home from time to time."
    l "No lo soy, pero de vez en cuando siento curiosidad por lo que ocurre en mi país."

# game/episode021.rpy:1123
translate spanish ep021_lilly_talk_0822a93a:

#   c "You’re checking on the news feeds on Tuolovi?"
    c "¿Estás comprobando las noticias de Tuolovi?"

# game/episode021.rpy:1125
translate spanish ep021_lilly_talk_ef96b952:

#   l "Sporadically, but nothing much is happening there."
    l "Esporádicamente, pero allí no pasa gran cosa."

# game/episode021.rpy:1126
translate spanish ep021_lilly_talk_96650821:

#   l "At least not things involving our family."
    l "Al menos no cosas que involucren a nuestra familia."

# game/episode021.rpy:1127
translate spanish ep021_lilly_talk_dc1ddb76:

#   l "There’s a lot about the Sovereignty though."
    l "Sin embargo, hay mucho sobre la Soberanía."

# game/episode021.rpy:1128
translate spanish ep021_lilly_talk_06854f1d:

#   c "More so than normal?"
    c "¿Más de lo normal?"

# game/episode021.rpy:1130
translate spanish ep021_lilly_talk_061ac71b:

#   l "Yes, unfortunately."
    l "Sí, por desgracia."

# game/episode021.rpy:1131
translate spanish ep021_lilly_talk_2174a494:

#   l "Apparently, other alien nations are following developments in the Sovereignty with suspicion."
    l "Al parecer, otras naciones extranjeras siguen con recelo la evolución de la Soberanía."

# game/episode021.rpy:1132
translate spanish ep021_lilly_talk_15f7e731:

#   c "Nothing new there."
    c "Nada nuevo."

# game/episode021.rpy:1134
translate spanish ep021_lilly_talk_338cdb9d:

#   l "No, but this time there actually seems to be something afoot."
    l "No, pero esta vez parece que hay algo en marcha."

# game/episode021.rpy:1135
translate spanish ep021_lilly_talk_d8765b2f:

#   l "Several sources are reporting massive troop redeployments and the Sovereignty shipyards have also geared up production."
    l "Varias fuentes informan de redespliegues masivos de tropas y los astilleros Sovereignty también han puesto en marcha la producción."

# game/episode021.rpy:1136
translate spanish ep021_lilly_talk_bed6f507:

#   c "Getting ready to stir some shit, no doubt."
    c "Preparándose para remover algo de mierda, sin duda."

# game/episode021.rpy:1137
translate spanish ep021_lilly_talk_cd87a2a4:

#   l "Yeah."
    l "Sí."

# game/episode021.rpy:1138
translate spanish ep021_lilly_talk_98361226:

#   l "Apparently there hasn’t been a production increase like this in several decades."
    l "Al parecer, no ha habido un aumento de la producción como éste en varias décadas."

# game/episode021.rpy:1139
translate spanish ep021_lilly_talk_8cf0837e:

#   c "The Sovereignty is looking to expand their borders then, probably?"
    c "Entonces, ¿el Soberano quiere ampliar sus fronteras?"

# game/episode021.rpy:1141
translate spanish ep021_lilly_talk_294f22da:

#   l "Probably."
    l "Probablemente."

# game/episode021.rpy:1142
translate spanish ep021_lilly_talk_518b4314:

#   l "Government sources say it’s to combat domestic terrorism."
    l "Fuentes gubernamentales dicen que es para combatir el terrorismo doméstico."

# game/episode021.rpy:1143
translate spanish ep021_lilly_talk_ff4821af:

#   c "Ah yes, that old chestnut."
    c "Ah, sí, esa vieja historia."

# game/episode021.rpy:1144
translate spanish ep021_lilly_talk_06f3a5b7:

#   l "There might be some truth in it."
    l "Puede que haya algo de verdad en ello."

# game/episode021.rpy:1145
translate spanish ep021_lilly_talk_7e5cd87f:

#   l "Several reports about a group called the Auric Exemplar claiming responsibility for terrorist attacks throughout the Sovereignty."
    l "Varios informes sobre un grupo llamado Auric Exemplar que reivindica la autoría de atentados terroristas en toda la Soberanía."

# game/episode021.rpy:1146
translate spanish ep021_lilly_talk_d1659317:

#   c "Terrorist attacks?"
    c "¿Ataques terroristas?"

# game/episode021.rpy:1148
translate spanish ep021_lilly_talk_6a502405:

#   l "Bombings, theft, you name it."
    l "Atentados, robos, de todo."

# game/episode021.rpy:1149
translate spanish ep021_lilly_talk_af5abeae:

#   l "No civilian casualties so far though."
    l "Sin embargo, hasta ahora no ha habido víctimas civiles."

# game/episode021.rpy:1150
translate spanish ep021_lilly_talk_3c68b6c0:

#   c "I thought those Exemplar were a fairytale."
    c "Pensaba que esos Exemplar eran un cuento de hadas."

# game/episode021.rpy:1151
translate spanish ep021_lilly_talk_f304a03e:

#   c "Or at the most, a group of stuffy university professors raving about violent dissent, without leaving the comfort of their homes."
    c "O, como mucho, un grupo de estirados profesores universitarios delirando sobre la disidencia violenta, sin salir de la comodidad de sus casas."

# game/episode021.rpy:1153
translate spanish ep021_lilly_talk_b88897a0:

#   l "That was my view of them as well, but apparently that has all changed."
    l "Yo también los veía así, pero parece que todo ha cambiado."

# game/episode021.rpy:1154
translate spanish ep021_lilly_talk_4f332b3e:

#   l "Or somebody took those theories about violent dissent and put them into practice."
    l "O alguien tomó esas teorías sobre la disidencia violenta y las puso en práctica."

# game/episode021.rpy:1155
translate spanish ep021_lilly_talk_a7da18b1:

#   c "Either way, I don’t think the Sovereignty is building a fleet to weed out terrorists."
    c "En cualquier caso, no creo que la Soberanía esté construyendo una flota para eliminar terroristas."

# game/episode021.rpy:1157
translate spanish ep021_lilly_talk_ef0e4a9c:

#   l "Me neither, it’s likely an excuse."
    l "Yo tampoco, es probable que sea una excusa."

# game/episode021.rpy:1158
translate spanish ep021_lilly_talk_e2bda4a3:

#   c "Regardless if it’s all true, if you learn anything else useful in those reports, let me know."
    c "Independientemente de si todo es cierto, si aprendes algo más útil en esos informes, házmelo saber."

# game/episode021.rpy:1160
translate spanish ep021_lilly_talk_6067bdda:

#   l "I will."
    l "Lo haré."

# game/episode021.rpy:1167
translate spanish ep021_celine_talk_8e142f22:

#   "Céline had told me to come to the computer room at the top of the compound."
    "Céline me había dicho que fuera a la sala de ordenadores de la parte superior del recinto."

# game/episode021.rpy:1168
translate spanish ep021_celine_talk_701b1e5c:

#   "She was there working with Jade to get access to the computer records."
    "Estaba allí trabajando con Jade para acceder a los registros informáticos."

# game/episode021.rpy:1169
translate spanish ep021_celine_talk_15b7144d:

#   "When I entered it turned out she was all alone."
    "Cuando entré resultó que estaba sola."

# game/episode021.rpy:1170
translate spanish ep021_celine_talk_d2536737:

#   c "Hey, I thought Jade was with you?"
    c "Oye, pensé que Jade estaba contigo."

# game/episode021.rpy:1172
translate spanish ep021_celine_talk_2e96ac19:

#   ce "Jade was working for five hours straight, so she’s having a lie down."
    ce "Jade estuvo trabajando cinco horas seguidas, así que está descansando."

# game/episode021.rpy:1173
translate spanish ep021_celine_talk_fb236d8d:

#   ce "And now I’m here all alone."
    ce "Y ahora estoy aquí sola."

# game/episode021.rpy:1174
translate spanish ep021_celine_talk_e401a02e:

#   c "Feeling lonely then, are you?"
    c "¿Te sientes solo?"

# game/episode021.rpy:1176
translate spanish ep021_celine_talk_acbe700f:

#   ce "Lonely and a little bored."
    ce "Solitario y un poco aburrido."

# game/episode021.rpy:1177
translate spanish ep021_celine_talk_cb75c10d:

#   c "The work going okay?"
    c "¿El trabajo va bien?"

# game/episode021.rpy:1178
translate spanish ep021_celine_talk_b8198a1b:

#   ce "Yes, we’re making progress."
    ce "Sí, estamos progresando."

# game/episode021.rpy:1179
translate spanish ep021_celine_talk_9252bc91:

#   ce "But it’s Jade who’s doing all the heavy lifting."
    ce "Pero es Jade quien está haciendo todo el trabajo pesado."

# game/episode021.rpy:1180
translate spanish ep021_celine_talk_f7fdba40:

#   ce "I never realized she was so good with the digital stuff."
    ce "No me había dado cuenta de que era tan buena con las cosas digitales."

# game/episode021.rpy:1181
translate spanish ep021_celine_talk_e6e240ac:

#   c "Yes, I was surprised as well when I learned of her hobby."
    c "Sí, yo también me sorprendí cuando me enteré de su afición."

# game/episode021.rpy:1183
translate spanish ep021_celine_talk_f3ca6dab:

#   ce "Doesn’t seem like a hobby to me anymore."
    ce "Ya no me parece un hobby."

# game/episode021.rpy:1184
translate spanish ep021_celine_talk_f83e0233:

#   c "No, I agree."
    c "No, estoy de acuerdo."

# game/episode021.rpy:1185
translate spanish ep021_celine_talk_d08847b1:

#   c "Her skills are pretty essential."
    c "Sus habilidades son bastante esenciales."

# game/episode021.rpy:1186
translate spanish ep021_celine_talk_fed8d564:

#   c "As are yours of course."
    c "Como los tuyos, por supuesto."

# game/episode021.rpy:1187
translate spanish ep021_celine_talk_b07459c0:

#   c "I don’t know how far we’d gotten without you as a pilot."
    c "No sé hasta dónde habríamos llegado sin ti como piloto."

# game/episode021.rpy:1188
translate spanish ep021_celine_talk_42fbfba3:

#   ce "Thanks."
    ce "Gracias."

# game/episode021.rpy:1191
translate spanish ep021_celine_talk_5cd939d0:

#   c "Crazy view out there."
    c "Qué vista más loca."

# game/episode021.rpy:1192
translate spanish ep021_celine_talk_bdd9fc6e:

#   ce "You can say that again."
    ce "Puedes repetirlo."

# game/episode021.rpy:1194
translate spanish ep021_celine_talk_952c075b:

#   ce "But it still seems like a dead landscape to me."
    ce "Pero me sigue pareciendo un paisaje muerto."

# game/episode021.rpy:1195
translate spanish ep021_celine_talk_306153eb:

#   c "It probably is."
    c "Probablemente lo sea."

# game/episode021.rpy:1196
translate spanish ep021_celine_talk_a0b58d2b:

#   c "I take it you’re not eager to stay here on Petrarch?"
    c "¿Supongo que no quieres quedarte en Petrarca?"

# game/episode021.rpy:1198
translate spanish ep021_celine_talk_274ec67a:

#   ce "No, not at all."
    ce "No, en absoluto."

# game/episode021.rpy:1199
translate spanish ep021_celine_talk_c0d8a610:

#   c "I think that’s the general sentiment."
    c "Creo que ese es el sentimiento general."

# game/episode021.rpy:1200
translate spanish ep021_celine_talk_9a37bfa6:

#   c "Well, I’ll let you get back to work."
    c "Bueno, te dejaré volver al trabajo."

# game/episode021.rpy:1201
translate spanish ep021_celine_talk_47286829:

#   ce "Thanks, see you around, [p_name_short]."
    ce "Gracias, nos vemos, [p_name_short]."

# game/episode021.rpy:1202
translate spanish ep021_celine_talk_b092993f:

#   c "You too."
    c "Tú también."

# game/episode021.rpy:1212
translate spanish ep021_eva_talk_6b3c1be0:

#   "Most of the crew was scattered throughout the complex, investigating the machinery that was seemingly left behind by whomever first built the compounds on Petrarch."
    "La mayor parte de la tripulación estaba dispersa por el complejo, investigando la maquinaria que al parecer dejaron los primeros que construyeron los complejos en Petrarch."

# game/episode021.rpy:1214
translate spanish ep021_eva_talk_cb8cd549:

#   "I was enjoying a moment of rest, when Eva suddenly marched through the door."
    "Estaba disfrutando de un momento de descanso, cuando Eva entró de repente por la puerta."

# game/episode021.rpy:1215
translate spanish ep021_eva_talk_371821c2:

#   e "[p_name_short]!"
    e "¡[p_name_short]!"

# game/episode021.rpy:1216
translate spanish ep021_eva_talk_05eb8c9b:

#   e "It’s happened!!!"
    e "¡¡¡Ha sucedido!!!"

# game/episode021.rpy:1217
translate spanish ep021_eva_talk_499819e9:

#   c "What happened?"
    c "¿Qué ha pasado?"

# game/episode021.rpy:1219
translate spanish ep021_eva_talk_bf410c69:

#   e "I did a test!"
    e "¡Hice una prueba!"

# game/episode021.rpy:1220
translate spanish ep021_eva_talk_0af78c5d:

#   e "[p_name_short], I’m pregnant!"
    e "[p_name_short]¡Estoy embarazada!"

# game/episode021.rpy:1224
translate spanish ep021_eva_talk_3dd5ee39:

#   c "What?!"
    c "¡¿Qué?!"

# game/episode021.rpy:1225
translate spanish ep021_eva_talk_4067b648:

#   c "Eva, that’s such great news, and so soon as well."
    c "Eva, qué buena noticia, y además tan pronto."

# game/episode021.rpy:1226
translate spanish ep021_eva_talk_d7a5edba:

#   e "I’m so happy!"
    e "¡Estoy tan feliz!"

# game/episode021.rpy:1229
translate spanish ep021_eva_talk_06c4a01e:

#   "I kissed my sister and together we lay down on the bed."
    "Besé a mi hermana y juntas nos tumbamos en la cama."

# game/episode021.rpy:1231
translate spanish ep021_eva_talk_14d4135a:

#   "I kissed Eva and together we lay down on the bed."
    "Besé a Eva y juntos nos tumbamos en la cama."

# game/episode021.rpy:1233
translate spanish ep021_eva_talk_b398fb49:

#   e "I didn’t get my period this month, so I started hoping right away."
    e "Este mes no me vino la regla, así que empecé a tener esperanzas enseguida."

# game/episode021.rpy:1234
translate spanish ep021_eva_talk_12554410:

#   e "Stupid, I know."
    e "Estúpido, lo sé."

# game/episode021.rpy:1235
translate spanish ep021_eva_talk_7a988ed3:

#   e "I kept debating whether to take a test, but our journey didn’t seem like the best time."
    e "Seguía debatiéndome si hacerme una prueba, pero nuestro viaje no parecía el mejor momento."

# game/episode021.rpy:1236
translate spanish ep021_eva_talk_375c9c28:

#   e "I can’t believe I’m pregnant already!"
    e "¡No puedo creer que ya esté embarazada!"

# game/episode021.rpy:1237
translate spanish ep021_eva_talk_ac2bea30:

#   c "Me neither."
    c "Yo tampoco."

# game/episode021.rpy:1238
translate spanish ep021_eva_talk_768d4681:

#   c "Do you know when it might have happened?"
    c "¿Sabe cuándo pudo ocurrir?"

# game/episode021.rpy:1240
translate spanish ep021_eva_talk_e554e3e6:

#   e "It must have been the first time we’ve been intimate together, after we escaped that desert planet."
    e "Debe haber sido la primera vez que hemos intimado juntos, después de escapar de ese planeta desierto."

# game/episode021.rpy:1241
translate spanish ep021_eva_talk_e1b4d79d:

#   c "Damn, talk about lucky shots..."
    c "Maldición, hablando de golpes de suerte..."

# game/episode021.rpy:1243
translate spanish ep021_eva_talk_98b8f99f:

#   e "Haha, yes!"
    e "Jaja, ¡sí!"

# game/episode021.rpy:1244
translate spanish ep021_eva_talk_b86ad017:

#   e "Very lucky."
    e "Mucha suerte."

# game/episode021.rpy:1246
translate spanish ep021_eva_talk_33969893:

#   e "I’m so happy, [p_name_short]!"
    e "¡Estoy tan feliz, [p_name_short]!"

# game/episode021.rpy:1247
translate spanish ep021_eva_talk_c5531862:

#   c "Me too!"
    c "¡Yo también!"

# game/episode021.rpy:1249
translate spanish ep021_eva_talk_a5e3e1aa:

#   e "Though it’s going to be a challenge, with everything happening."
    e "Aunque va a ser un reto, con todo lo que está pasando."

# game/episode021.rpy:1250
translate spanish ep021_eva_talk_f588fff4:

#   e "We’re still being hunted."
    e "Todavía nos persiguen."

# game/episode021.rpy:1251
translate spanish ep021_eva_talk_6e1ba734:

#   c "We’ll figure something out."
    c "Ya se nos ocurrirá algo."

# game/episode021.rpy:1253
translate spanish ep021_eva_talk_a73407a9:

#   e "But in a few months I’ll be fat, hormonal and useless."
    e "Pero en unos meses estaré gorda, hormonada e inútil."

# game/episode021.rpy:1254
translate spanish ep021_eva_talk_221a31a0:

#   c "No you won’t."
    c "No, no lo harás."

# game/episode021.rpy:1255
translate spanish ep021_eva_talk_83444c11:

#   c "You’re going to be a beautiful mother, Eva."
    c "Vas a ser una madre preciosa, Eva."

